<br />
1456 Verge of the Mindless Servant
<br />

<br />
Now, remember AAs will offset the above data. If you have Harmonious Attack and all your dual wield AA - it will favor the damage/delay. But then again, weapon affinity will push you back toward big procs....</span></td>
